data.description: Welcome to your dream home - a stunning like-new build from 2020! Inside, you'll be greeted by an open floorplan with plenty of flex space to suit your needs. With three nicely-sized bedrooms downstairs, including a master with an extra-large closet, you'll have all the space you need to relax and unwind. The 4th bedroom upstairs comes complete with a private bath, making it the perfect guest suite. But that's not all - this home also has amazing under the stairs storage that could double as a home office or reading nook, providing you with even more versatility. The covered patio is the perfect spot to enjoy an outdoor meal or entertain guests, while the 2 car garage provides ample space for your vehicles. See it today!
